NAME
       pnmfile - replaced by pamfile

DESCRIPTION
       This program is part of Netpbm(1).

       pnmfile  was replaced in Netpbm 10.9 (September 2002) by
       pamfile(1).

       pamfile is backward compatible with pnmfile,  but  works
       on PAM images too.
